data.description: 1,832 Sq Ft of pure Paradise. This 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom House has a 2019 AC, 2015 roof, huge Lanai, backyard and 2 car garage. The whole house has been upgraded and feels so spacious (2,526 Sq Ft.). Come "Live The Dream" and join the very Active Community of Conquistador Estates with tennis/pickelball and shuffleboard Courts and a Fishing Pier on the Saint Lucie River. The resort-style clubhouse has a large ballroom (with Kitchen), card rooms, exercise room and Library. This Community also has a workroom for those that enjoy woodworking, carpentry, etc. This house is spectacular!
